%p
  Hi #{@user.first_name || @user.name},

%p
  You recently uploaded transcript files to Nabu that have not yet been mapped
  to the media files they annotate. Annotation mappings let downstream tools
  (and the RO-Crate metadata) pair each transcript with its media — without
  them, the relationship is lost.

%p Please take a moment to record the mappings:

- @items_with_unmapped.each do |item, essences|
  %h3
    = link_to "#{item.collection.identifier} / #{item.identifier}",
              collection_item_annotations_url(item.collection, item)
  %ul
    - essences.each do |essence|
      %li
        = link_to essence.filename,
                  collection_item_annotations_url(item.collection, item, anchor: "transcript-#{essence.id}")

%p
  Thanks,
  %br
  The Nabu team
